---
import { Font } from "astro:assets";
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

import IMG_gardenBackground from '../images/garden-background.webp';
import IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassSitting from '../images/sarahanddave_looking_glass_sitting.webp';
import IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassStanding from '../images/sarahanddave_looking_glass_standing.webp';

import IMG_Marley  from '../images/Marley.webp';
import IMG_Eleanor from '../images/Eleanor.webp';
import IMG_Teyla   from '../images/Teyla.webp';
import IMG_Donnie  from '../images/Donnie.webp';

const gardenBackground = `url("${IMG_gardenBackground.src}")`;

import RSVP from "../components/rsvp.astro"

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<!--Not sure why all the provided favicon files are not linked here...-->
		<link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon/favicon-16x16.png">
		<link rel="manifest" href="/favicon/site.webmanifest">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<Font cssVariable="--font-header" />
		<Font cssVariable="--font-primary" />
		<title>Sarah and David's Wedding | July 11, 2026 @ 5 PM</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="main-header" >
			<div id="sarah-main-name">
				<h2>SARAH ELIZABETH</h2>
				<h2>PR&Eacute;OT COVINGTON</h2>
			</div>
			<h3>&</h3>
			<div id="david-main-name">
				<h2>DAVID JEFFREY ADAMS</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="welcome-section">
			<h2>Saturday July 11th, 2026 @ 5PM</h2>
			<h3>Church of The Holy Communion</h3>
			<h4>218 Ashley Ave</h4>
			<h4>Charleston, SC 29403</h4>
			<hr/>
		</div>
		<div id="story-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">Our Story</h2>
			<p>
				It all started with a simple cup of coffee, 
				and somehow it evolved into a full-blown domestic ecosystem. Since that 
				first date, we’ve built a life filled with the things we love most: 
				Sarah tending to her garden, David dedicated to his writing practice, 
				and a home overflowing with books, music, and retro video games.
			</p>

			<Image class="center-image image-style-1" src={IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassSitting} alt="Sarah and David sitting at Looking Glass Falls, North Carolina"/>

			<p>
				When we aren’t out for long walks, we’re 
				busy serving our four demanding roommates. First, there is 
				<strong>Marley</strong>, our Shih Tzu who lives by a grueling schedule 
				of "walk, nap, repeat" (with several union-mandated snack breaks in 
				between). He is joined by <strong>Eleanor</strong>, a Victorian Duchess 
				who is deeply confused as to why she was reborn as a quadruped, and 
				<strong>Teyla</strong>, the rambunctious kitten currently in charge of 
				daily chaos. Finally, there’s <strong>Donnie</strong>, the Russian 
				Tortoise. Donnie has a very demanding, high-profile career as a 
				classroom pet.
			</p>

			<p>
				Whether we’re digging in the dirt, hitting 
				a word count goal, or trying to stay on Marley’s strict walking 
				rotation, we’ve discovered that life is just better together. We are 
				so excited to step away from the garden and the desk for a few hours 
				to celebrate the start of our next chapter with all of you!
			</p>

			<p><strong>We can't wait to see you there!</strong></p>

			<Image class="center-image image-style-1" src={IMG_sarahAndDaveLookingGlassStanding} alt="Sarah and David standing at Looking Glass Falls, North Carolina"/>




			<hr/>
		</div>
		<div id="family-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">Our Family</h2>
			<div class="pet-grid">
				<div class="pet-card">
					<div class="pet-img-wrap">
						<Image src={IMG_Marley}  alt="Marley, the Shih Tzu" />
					</div>
					<span class="pet-name">Marley</span>
				</div>
				<div class="pet-card">
					<div class="pet-img-wrap">
						<Image src={IMG_Eleanor} alt="Eleanor, the cat" />
					</div>
					<span class="pet-name">Eleanor</span>
				</div>
				<div class="pet-card">
					<div class="pet-img-wrap">
						<Image src={IMG_Teyla}   alt="Teyla, the kitten" />
					</div>
					<span class="pet-name">Teyla</span>
				</div>
				<div class="pet-card">
					<div class="pet-img-wrap">
						<Image src={IMG_Donnie}  alt="Donnie, the Russian Tortoise" />
					</div>
					<span class="pet-name">Donnie</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="expand-hint">Tap any photo to expand</p>
			<hr/>
		</div>
		<div id="honeymoon-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">Honeymoon Fund</h2>
			<p>
				Your presence at our wedding is the greatest gift of all! If you'd
				like to contribute to our honeymoon, we'd be incredibly grateful.
				Any amount is appreciated and will help us create memories to last
				a lifetime.
			</p>
			<div class="payment-buttons">
				<a href="https://venmo.com/u/SEPC36" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="venmo-button">
					<svg class="venmo-icon" viewBox="0 0 111 111" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
						<path fill="currentColor" d="M93.7 5C96.9 10.2 98.4 15.6 98.4 22.4C98.4 45.5 78.8 75.6 63 95H27.5L13 7.3L43.8 4.3L51.2 60.1C57.8 49.3 66 32.3 66 20.4C66 13.9 64.8 9.4 62.9 5.7L93.7 5Z"/>
					</svg>
					Venmo
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.paypal.me/DaveBuildsStuff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="paypal-button">
					<svg class="paypal-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
						<path fill="currentColor" d="M7.076 21.337H2.47a.641.641 0 0 1-.633-.74L4.944.901C5.026.382 5.474 0 5.998 0h7.46c2.57 0 4.578.543 5.69 1.81 1.01 1.15 1.304 2.42 1.012 4.287-.023.143-.047.288-.077.437-.983 5.05-4.349 6.797-8.647 6.797h-2.19c-.524 0-.968.382-1.05.9l-1.12 7.106zm14.146-14.42a3.35 3.35 0 0 0-.607-.541c-.013.076-.026.175-.041.254-.93 4.778-4.005 7.201-9.138 7.201h-2.19a.563.563 0 0 0-.556.479l-1.187 7.527h-.506l-.24 1.516a.56.56 0 0 0 .554.647h3.882c.46 0 .85-.334.922-.788.06-.26.76-4.852.816-5.09a.932.932 0 0 1 .923-.788h.58c3.76 0 6.705-1.528 7.565-5.946.36-1.847.174-3.388-.777-4.471z"/>
					</svg>
					PayPal
				</a>
				<a href="https://buy.stripe.com/9B628qb6OfI22AwbvifrW00" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="stripe-button">
					<span class="stripe-logo" aria-label="Stripe">
						<svg class="stripe-s" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
							<path fill="currentColor" d="M13.976 9.15c-2.172-.806-3.356-1.426-3.356-2.409 0-.831.683-1.305 1.901-1.305 2.227 0 4.515.858 6.09 1.631l.89-5.494C18.252.975 15.697 0 12.165 0 9.667 0 7.589.654 6.104 1.872 4.56 3.147 3.757 4.992 3.757 7.218c0 4.039 2.467 5.76 6.476 7.219 2.585.929 3.445 1.574 3.445 2.583 0 .98-.84 1.545-2.354 1.545-1.875 0-4.965-.921-6.99-2.109l-.9 5.555C5.175 22.99 8.385 24 11.714 24c2.641 0 4.843-.624 6.328-1.813 1.664-1.296 2.525-3.228 2.525-5.63 0-4.128-2.524-5.851-6.591-7.408z"/>
						</svg>
						<span class="stripe-wordmark">stripe</span>
					</span>
					<span class="card-icons">
						<span class="card-badge card-visa">VISA</span>
						<span class="card-badge card-mc">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 38 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-label="Mastercard">
								<circle cx="15" cy="12" r="10" fill="#eb001b"/>
								<circle cx="23" cy="12" r="10" fill="#f79e1b"/>
								<path d="M19 5.4a10 10 0 0 1 0 13.2A10 10 0 0 1 19 5.4z" fill="#ff5f00"/>
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge card-amex">AMEX</span>
						<span class="card-badge card-disc">
							DISC<svg viewBox="0 0 10 10" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="5" fill="#f76f20"/></svg>
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge card-wallet apple-pay-badge" hidden>
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
								<path fill="currentColor" d="M11.624 7.222c-.876 0-2.232-.996-3.66-.96-1.884.024-3.612 1.092-4.584 2.784-1.956 3.396-.504 8.412 1.404 11.172.936 1.348 2.04 2.856 3.504 2.8 1.404-.06 1.932-.912 3.636-.912 1.692 0 2.172.912 3.66.876 1.512-.024 2.472-1.368 3.396-2.724 1.068-1.56 1.512-3.072 1.536-3.156-.036-.012-2.94-1.128-2.976-4.488-.024-2.808 2.292-4.152 2.4-4.212-1.32-1.932-3.348-2.148-4.056-2.196-1.848-.144-3.396 1.008-4.26 1.008zm2.904-2.688c.78-.876 1.296-2.1 1.152-3.324-1.116.048-2.46.744-3.264 1.584-.72.768-1.344 2.016-1.176 3.216 1.236.096 2.508-.624 3.288-1.476"/>
							</svg>
							Pay
						</span>
						<span class="card-badge card-wallet google-pay-badge" hidden>
							<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
								<path fill="#4285F4" d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"/>
								<path fill="#34A853" d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"/>
								<path fill="#FBBC05" d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l3.66-2.84z"/>
								<path fill="#EA4335" d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"/>
							</svg>
							Pay
						</span>
					</span>
					<span class="stripe-label">Pay by Card<span class="apple-pay-label" hidden> | Apple Pay</span><span class="google-pay-label" hidden> | Google Pay</span></span>
				</a>
			</div>
			<hr/>
		</div>

		<div id="rsvp-section">
			<h2 class="section-header">RSVP</h2>
			<p>
				&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Please tell us if you will be attending below. If only some 
				members of your party will be coming, please let us know in the 
				notes.
			</p>
			<RSVP />
			<hr/>
		</div>

		<div id="lightbox">
			<img id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="" />
		</div>
		<button id="lightbox-prev"  aria-label="Previous image">&#8592;</button>
		<button id="lightbox-next"  aria-label="Next image">&#8594;</button>
		<button id="lightbox-close" aria-label="Close">&#x2715;</button>

		<button id="back-to-top" aria-label="Back to top">&#8593;</button>

		<footer>
			<p class="footer-names">Sarah &amp; David</p>
			<p class="footer-date">July 11, 2026</p>
		</footer>

	</body>
</html>

<style define:vars={{ gardenBackground }}>

	:root {
		--dark-blue-color: #0f1534;
		--light-blue-color: #345d87;
		--off-white-color: #ECECEC;
		--blue-green-color: #81c7a9;
		--brown-color: #625824;
	}

	html { 
	background: var(--gardenBackground) no-repeat center center fixed; 
	-webkit-background-size: cover;
	-moz-background-size: cover;
	-o-background-size: cover;
	background-size: cover;
	}

	body {
		height: 100%;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 1000px; /* Or a width in % or ch */
		margin: 0 auto;    /* Centers the section */
		background-color: #ECECEC99;
	}

	p {
		padding: 0px 100px 0px 100px;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}

	/*In case I decide to use HRs*/
	hr {
		
		display: none;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #606060; /* Darker charcoal option */  
		width: 25%;
	}

	#main-header {
		align-items: center;
		background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #162048, var(--dark-blue-color));
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		color: white;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.25rem;
		height: 22rem;
		justify-content: center;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 50% 20%;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 50% 20%;
		border-bottom: 3px solid var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	#main-header h2 {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		margin: 0;
	}

	#main-header h3 {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1.2rem;
		width: 65%;
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin: 0.4rem 0;
	}

	#main-header h3::before,
	#main-header h3::after {
		content: '';
		flex: 1;
		height: 1px;
		background: rgba(129, 199, 169, 0.5);
	}

	#sarah-main-name h2:first-of-type {
		margin-top: 40px;
	}

	#david-main-name h2 {
		margin-bottom: 40px;
	}

	#welcome-section {
		align-items: center;
		padding-top: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
	}

	#welcome-section h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}

	#welcome-section h3 {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
		color: var(--light-blue-color);
		margin: 0;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}

	#welcome-section h4 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0.2rem 0;
	}

	#story-section p:first-of-type::first-letter {
        float: left;
        font-family: var(--font-header);
        font-size: 6em;
        line-height: 0.72;
        padding-right: 12px;
        padding-top: 8px;
        color: var(--light-blue-color);
        font-weight: 400;
	}

	#family-section {
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.pet-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 1.5rem 100px 0.5rem 100px;
	}

	.pet-card {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.pet-img-wrap {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		border-radius: 50%;
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 3px solid var(--light-blue-color);
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
	}

	.pet-img-wrap:hover {
		border-color: var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	.pet-img-wrap img {
		cursor: zoom-in;
	}

	.pet-card {
		position: relative;
	}

	.expand-hint {
		display: none;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--light-blue-color);
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
	}

	.pet-img-wrap img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		display: block;
	}

	.pet-name {
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--light-blue-color);
		letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
	}

	#honeymoon-section {
		padding-bottom: 10px;
	}

	.payment-buttons {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
		width: 280px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.venmo-button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		width: 100%;
		background-color: #3D95CE;
		color: white;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.03rem;
		padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		border: 3px solid transparent;
		transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.venmo-button:hover {
		background-color: #2d7ab5;
		border-color: var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	.venmo-icon, .paypal-icon {
		width: 1.4rem;
		height: 1.4rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.stripe-button {
		display: inline-flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		width: 100%;
		background-color: #3D95CE;
		color: white;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.03rem;
		padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		border: 3px solid transparent;
		transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.stripe-button:hover {
		background-color: #2d7ab5;
		border-color: var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	.stripe-logo {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.4rem;
	}

	.stripe-s {
		width: 1.3rem;
		height: 1.3rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.stripe-wordmark {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-family: sans-serif;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.stripe-label {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		opacity: 0.85;
		letter-spacing: 0.04rem;
	}

	.paypal-button {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		width: 100%;
		background-color: #3D95CE;
		color: white;
		font-family: var(--font-primary);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: 0.03rem;
		padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		border: 3px solid transparent;
		transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.paypal-button:hover {
		background-color: #2d7ab5;
		border-color: var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	.card-icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.35rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.card-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.2rem;
		font-size: 0.6rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: 0.04rem;
		padding: 0.15rem 0.35rem;
		border-radius: 3px;
		background: white;
		color: #333;
		height: 1.4rem;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	.card-visa {
		color: #1a1f71;
		font-style: italic;
		font-size: 0.7rem;
	}

	.card-mc svg {
		width: 1.6rem;
		height: 1rem;
	}

	.card-amex {
		background: #016fd0;
		color: white;
	}

	.card-disc {
		gap: 0.25rem;
	}

	.card-disc svg {
		width: 0.6rem;
		height: 0.6rem;
	}

	[hidden] { display: none !important; }

	.card-wallet {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.2rem;
		background: #1c1c1e;
		color: white;
	}

	.card-wallet svg {
		width: 0.85rem;
		height: 0.85rem;
	}

	#rsvp-section {
		padding-bottom: 50px;
	}

	.center-image {
		display: block;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.image-style-1 {
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 3px solid var(--light-blue-color);
		margin-top: 30px;
		margin-bottom: 30px;
		width: 700px;
		height: auto;
		transition: border-color 0.2s;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.image-style-1:hover {
		border-color: var(--blue-green-color);
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align:left;
		font-family: var(--font-header);
		font-size: 38px;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0px;
		margin-left: 100px;
